{"tid":672603,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"入咗院 屎忽痕你問我答","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T23:23:55.000Z","uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e660df46f02008d2da62595e0b3bf9d18da4fc0b","tid":672603,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"今日9點幾入咗院 <br />\n之後都係無無聊咁坐 <br />\n不過帶咗啲嘢做 冇咁悶<br />\n星期三先做手術 仲有幾個漫漫長夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是就順手開個post記錄下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲可以叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a376636bd0612727fdd2fcaa1af123a42c4bdc1","tid":672603,"uid":133529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"香港醫院好似好少做變性手術喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439aab67d15410905ca305ed3dfd21a27698f568","tid":672603,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a376636bd0612727fdd2fcaa1af123a42c4bdc1","tid":672603,"uid":133529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"香港醫院好似好少做變性手術喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f586aaeb262577e0d8958cb96bead11add2787","tid":672603,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"三圍"},{"pid":"fac3b6d876afc3bb308e3c2da4d3a119e5d22bf1","tid":672603,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"27f586aaeb262577e0d8958cb96bead11add2787","tid":672603,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"三圍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"我冇度，你幫下我度好冇？"},{"pid":"979ddcb5ab3da8dfb8b0fdfc5ce72242d4e41c18","tid":672603,"uid":2419,"l